Examining the relationship with elevation

prec.sf$elev <- st_extract(dtm, prec.sf) %>% pull(1)
ggplot(prec.sf, aes(x=elev, y=Jul)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(se=T) +
  labs(x="Elevation (m a. s.)", y="Precipitation (mm)")
